響透<br />\n建自由 光輝香港<br />\n<br />\nB<br />\n在晚星 墜落徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣智慧 也永不滅<br />\n<br />\nA3<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求民主 與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"e4eef97a13fbc519521df5e5da831d765c56ae74","tid":1574320,"uid":262802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e07ec06f4dc9195f57ae50d66fc4a351d3e5fb46","tid":1574320,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"自己係youtube搵 搵完上呢個網轉mp3<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtubeto.com/m/zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtubeto.com%2Fm%2Fzh%2F&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c5151ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtubeto.com/m/zh/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"唔該曬"},{"pid":"bcc4b2f1e9998797945b831d98be0f2ed8a9dc1a","tid":1574320,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"發？<br />\nSend<br />\n連登用錯字好大罪架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc7a5f0e1b3bbf304647c25024d3c2b1ca85d95","tid":1574320,"uid":262802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc4b2f1e9998797945b831d98be0f2ed8a9dc1a","tid":1574320,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"發？<br />\nSend<br />\n連登用錯字好大罪架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"發同send唔係一樣？"},{"pid":"8b5ef5f9c77ed02f7371c7311ed59b90c642aac5","tid":1574320,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc7a5f0e1b3bbf304647c25024d3c2b1ca85d95","tid":1574320,"uid":262802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcc4b2f1e9998797945b831d98be0f2ed8a9dc1a","tid":1574320,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"發？<br />\nSend<br />\n連登用錯字